    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎光临！在这里，您将体验策略对决的刺激: 格挡攻击、获取弹药、射击对手。祝您玩得愉快！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏规则</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规则与石头剪刀布类似：双方玩家同时做出决策，拥有三个可选指令：格挡、获取弹药、射击。玩家需要先获取弹药才能射击，但若在获取弹药时遭对手射击，则会被击中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>好友对战或随机匹配</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301930/extras/7fa2e7367a234261222c8e84f5529921.poster.avif?t=1765901197\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301930/extras/7fa2e7367a234261222c8e84f5529921.webm?t=1765901197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301930/extras/7fa2e7367a234261222c8e84f5529921.mp4?t=1765901197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >既可邀请好友一较高下，也可通过智能匹配系统与全球玩家切磋！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>技能卡牌</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301930/extras/6dd585ccfc4df48fd48e8db414657ba5.poster.avif?t=1765901197\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301930/extras/6dd585ccfc4df48fd48e8db414657ba5.webm?t=1765901197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301930/extras/6dd585ccfc4df48fd48e8db414657ba5.mp4?t=1765901197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用能扭转战局的强力技能卡，在对决中占据上风。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>面部编辑</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301930/extras/cb49b026074180a41f82f05e3a9ee652.poster.avif?t=1765901197\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301930/extras/cb49b026074180a41f82f05e3a9ee652.webm?t=1765901197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们深知自我表达的重要性。精心定制您的头盔造型，向世界展现真实自我——或至少是您想要呈现的模样。</p>",
